{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "it_ops", "channel": "incident_reports", "user": "emily_patel", "message": "Hello team, I'm thrilled to announce that our IT department has achieved a significant goal for Q1 2025. We've reached a 98% response rate to all internal helpdesk tickets. This is an incredible testament to our commitment to operational reliability and support across MediConn Solutions. Great job everyone!", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "it_ops", "channel": "incident_reports", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "That's fantastic news, Emily! It really shows how much we've improved our processes and responsiveness. Let's aim to keep this up or even better in the next quarter!", "create_at": 1620500500000}}
